---
export const prerender = true;
import LightLayout from '../layouts/LightLayout.astro';
import { ICON_PATHS } from '../data/icons';
---

<LightLayout title="Expose — Article Context · by Lattice">
  <main class="relative z-10 max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 bg-retro-bg">

    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <div class="mb-8 text-[10px] font-mono text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-[0.22em] flex items-center gap-3">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-retro-ink transition">Lattice</a>
      <span class="text-retro-ink/20">/</span>
      <span class="text-retro-ink">Expose</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Doc header -->
    <div class="border-t border-retro-ink/15 pt-3 flex items-center justify-between text-[9px] font-mono text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-10">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-5">
        <span>EXPOSE · v0.2</span>
        <span class="hidden md:inline">Context utility · 5 rich-dossier demo entities</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-retro-green"></span>
        <span>Public beta</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <header class="mb-16">
      <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-retro-green uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-3">A Lattice product</div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-semibold text-retro-ink tracking-tight leading-[1.05] mb-5">
        Expose <span class="italic font-light text-retro-green">— the hidden context behind every name.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-retro-slate leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-8">
        Read any news article. Expose underlines the politicians, companies, media outlets and think tanks being mentioned. Hover for a compact context card. Click to pin a full dossier — ownership chains, donor fingerprints, voting-rhetoric gaps, hidden relationships — every claim source-linked and confidence-scored.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="#install" class="bg-retro-green text-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-retro-ledger transition-colors rounded-sm shadow-[3px_3px_0px_rgba(15,61,46,1)] hover:shadow-none hover:translate-x-[3px] hover:translate-y-[3px]">
          Install Expose
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/annamariawettstein/remove-barriers/tree/annamariawettstein/copy-repo-aesthetic/extension" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-retro-ink border border-retro-ink bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-retro-bg transition rounded-sm">
          View source →
        </a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Demo: hover-card preview -->
    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-[10px] font-mono text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-retro-green" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" set:html={ICON_PATHS.search} />
        What you see
      </h2>

      <div class="bg-white border border-retro-border rounded-md p-6 lg:p-10 mb-6">
        <!-- Mocked article paragraph with underlined entities -->
        <p class="text-base text-retro-ink leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          Speaking on Monday, <span class="expose-demo-entity">Keir Starmer</span> defended the new procurement strategy. Critics pointed at <span class="expose-demo-entity">Serco</span>, a major government contractor, and the <span class="expose-demo-entity">Institute of Economic Affairs</span>, whose recent paper appears to echo the policy language. Coverage was led by <span class="expose-demo-entity">The Guardian</span>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Three card previews side-by-side with confidence pills -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <!-- Politician card preview -->
        <div class="bg-retro-bg border border-retro-ink rounded-sm p-4 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_rgba(15,61,46,0.95)]">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-retro-slate mb-2">
            <span class="text-retro-green font-semibold">POLITICIAN</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-retro-ink">lattice</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-base font-semibold text-retro-ink mb-0.5">Keir Starmer</div>
          <div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">LAB · Holborn and St Pancras</div>
          <div class="border-t border-retro-border pt-3 space-y-3 text-[12px]">
            <div>
              <div class="font-mono text-[9px] text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Top donor sector</div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                <span class="font-semibold">Finance &amp; business</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-[8px] uppercase tracking-widest px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full border" style="color:#0f5132;border-color:#0f5132;background:rgba(15,81,50,0.08);">high</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-[9px] font-mono text-retro-green mt-1">Electoral Commission ↗</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-mono text-[9px] text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Rhetoric-vs-vote flags</div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                <span class="font-semibold">2 surfaced</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-[8px] uppercase tracking-widest px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full border" style="color:#8a5a00;border-color:#8a5a00;background:rgba(138,90,0,0.08);">medium</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-[9px] font-mono text-retro-green mt-1">Hansard / Public Whip ↗</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Company card preview -->
        <div class="bg-retro-bg border border-retro-ink rounded-sm p-4 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_rgba(15,61,46,0.95)]">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-retro-slate mb-2">
            <span class="text-retro-green font-semibold">COMPANY</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-retro-ink">lattice</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-base font-semibold text-retro-ink mb-0.5">Serco</div>
          <div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Outsourcing / public services</div>
          <div class="border-t border-retro-border pt-3 space-y-3 text-[12px]">
            <div>
              <div class="font-mono text-[9px] text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Gov contract exposure</div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                <span class="font-semibold">High</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-[8px] uppercase tracking-widest px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full border" style="color:#0f5132;border-color:#0f5132;background:rgba(15,81,50,0.08);">high</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-[9px] font-mono text-retro-green mt-1">Contracts Finder ↗</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-mono text-[9px] text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Lobbying footprint</div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                <span class="font-semibold">Declared</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-[8px] uppercase tracking-widest px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full border" style="color:#8a5a00;border-color:#8a5a00;background:rgba(138,90,0,0.08);">medium</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-[9px] font-mono text-retro-green mt-1">Register of Consultant Lobbyists ↗</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Think tank card preview -->
        <div class="bg-retro-bg border border-retro-ink rounded-sm p-4 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_rgba(15,61,46,0.95)]">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-retro-slate mb-2">
            <span class="text-retro-green font-semibold">THINK TANK</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-retro-ink">lattice</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-base font-semibold text-retro-ink mb-0.5">Institute of Economic Affairs</div>
          <div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Policy network</div>
          <div class="border-t border-retro-border pt-3 space-y-3 text-[12px]">
            <div>
              <div class="font-mono text-[9px] text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Policy influence</div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                <span class="font-semibold">Indirect, recurring</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-[8px] uppercase tracking-widest px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full border" style="color:#8a5a00;border-color:#8a5a00;background:rgba(138,90,0,0.08);">medium</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-[9px] font-mono text-retro-green mt-1">Published reports / Hansard ↗</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-mono text-[9px] text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Funding transparency</div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                <span class="font-semibold">Partial</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-[8px] uppercase tracking-widest px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full border" style="color:#8b1e3f;border-color:#8b1e3f;background:rgba(139,30,63,0.08);">low</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-[9px] font-mono text-retro-green mt-1">Organisation disclosures ↗</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-[12px] text-retro-slate italic">Click any underlined name in the actual extension and a pinned right-side dossier opens with the full sections, relationships, and follow toggle.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- How it works -->
    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-[10px] font-mono text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-retro-green" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" set:html={ICON_PATHS.summary} />
        How it works
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-5">
        <div class="bg-white border border-retro-border rounded-md p-6">
          <div class="font-mono text-2xl text-retro-green mb-4 border border-retro-green/30 bg-retro-green/5 w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm">01</div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-retro-ink mb-2">Browse anywhere</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-retro-slate leading-relaxed">Runs on every page. Static articles, SPAs, social feeds — a MutationObserver re-scans whenever the page changes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-retro-border rounded-md p-6">
          <div class="font-mono text-2xl text-retro-green mb-4 border border-retro-green/30 bg-retro-green/5 w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm">02</div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-retro-ink mb-2">Hover · compact card</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-retro-slate leading-relaxed">A small card surfaces the top 2–3 metrics. Each fact carries a confidence label (high / medium / low) and a source link.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-retro-border rounded-md p-6">
          <div class="font-mono text-2xl text-retro-green mb-4 border border-retro-green/30 bg-retro-green/5 w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm">03</div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-retro-ink mb-2">Click · pinned dossier</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-retro-slate leading-relaxed">A right-side panel opens. Full sections: donor fingerprint, ownership web, voting-rhetoric gaps, board overlap — plus relationships, each clearly scored.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-retro-border rounded-md p-6">
          <div class="font-mono text-2xl text-retro-green mb-4 border border-retro-green/30 bg-retro-green/5 w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm">04</div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-retro-ink mb-2">Follow what matters</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-retro-slate leading-relaxed">Tap "Follow this thread" inside any dossier. Your tracked entities sync via Chrome storage — alerts when filings change is the next milestone.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Entities tracked -->
    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-[10px] font-mono text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-retro-green" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" set:html={ICON_PATHS.people} />
        Currently tracked
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 border-t border-retro-border pt-6">
        <div>
          <p class="text-[9px] font-mono text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Politicians</p>
          <p class="text-3xl font-semibold text-retro-ink mb-1">2</p>
          <p class="text-[11px] font-mono text-retro-slate">Starmer · Farage</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-[9px] font-mono text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Company</p>
          <p class="text-3xl font-semibold text-retro-ink mb-1">1</p>
          <p class="text-[11px] font-mono text-retro-slate">Serco (gov contractor)</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-[9px] font-mono text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">News outlet</p>
          <p class="text-3xl font-semibold text-retro-ink mb-1">1</p>
          <p class="text-[11px] font-mono text-retro-slate">The Guardian (trust-owned)</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-[9px] font-mono text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Think tank</p>
          <p class="text-3xl font-semibold text-retro-ink mb-1">1</p>
          <p class="text-[11px] font-mono text-retro-slate">Institute of Economic Affairs</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-[11px] text-retro-slate italic">v0.2 ships with 5 deep-dossier demo entities to stress-test the schema and UX. Full Lattice graph (1.2M+ entities) lands with v1.0.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Install -->
    <section class="mb-20" id="install">
      <h2 class="text-[10px] font-mono text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-retro-green" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" set:html={ICON_PATHS.check} />
        Install
      </h2>
      <div class="bg-retro-ink text-white rounded-md p-8 lg:p-10">
        <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-retro-green uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-3">Beta · load as unpacked extension</div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">Five steps, Chrome / Edge / Brave</h3>
        <ol class="space-y-3 text-sm text-white/80 max-w-2xl mb-6">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-mono text-retro-green text-xs mt-1">01</span><span>Clone or download the <code class="text-white/90 bg-white/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-sm">extension/</code> folder from the Lattice repo</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-mono text-retro-green text-xs mt-1">02</span><span>Open <code class="text-white/90 bg-white/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-sm">chrome://extensions</code> in a Chromium-based browser</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-mono text-retro-green text-xs mt-1">03</span><span>Toggle <strong>Developer mode</strong> in the top-right</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-mono text-retro-green text-xs mt-1">04</span><span>Click <strong>Load unpacked</strong> and pick the <code class="text-white/90 bg-white/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-sm">extension/</code> folder</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-mono text-retro-green text-xs mt-1">05</span><span>Pin Expose to the toolbar. Visit any UK news article and look for dotted underlines</span></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-[0.18em]">Chrome Web Store listing · in review</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Roadmap -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-[10px] font-mono text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-retro-green" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" set:html={ICON_PATHS.calendar} />
        On the roadmap
      </h2>
      <ol class="border-l-2 border-retro-green/30 pl-6 space-y-5">
        <li class="relative">
          <span class="absolute -left-[31px] top-1.5 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-retro-green"></span>
          <p class="text-[10px] font-mono text-retro-green uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">v0.2 · now</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-retro-ink leading-relaxed">5 rich-dossier demo entities with structured sections + relationships. Hover card + pinned sidebar. Confidence scoring. MutationObserver-based SPA re-scanning. Follow-state via chrome.storage.sync.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="relative">
          <span class="absolute -left-[31px] top-1.5 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-retro-green/50"></span>
          <p class="text-[10px] font-mono text-retro-green uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">v0.3 · next</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-retro-ink leading-relaxed">Backend swap: live ingestion from Electoral Commission, Companies House, lobbying register, and TheyWorkForYou. Per-jurisdiction entity resolvers — no more exact-alias matching. Relationship scoring computed server-side.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="relative">
          <span class="absolute -left-[31px] top-1.5 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-retro-green/30"></span>
          <p class="text-[10px] font-mono text-retro-green uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">v0.4</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-retro-ink leading-relaxed">Watched-entity alerts when filings change. Export + comparison mode. Per-site allowlist.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="relative">
          <span class="absolute -left-[31px] top-1.5 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-retro-green/20"></span>
          <p class="text-[10px] font-mono text-retro-green uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">v1.0</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-retro-ink leading-relaxed">Chrome Web Store + Firefox + Safari. Saved investigations sync with the Lattice workspace.</p>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer strip -->
    <footer class="mt-16 pt-6 border-t border-retro-ink/15 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-2 md:items-center md:justify-between text-[9px] font-mono text-retro-slate uppercase tracking-[0.22em]">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <span>Expose · v0.2 public beta</span>
        <span>A Lattice product</span>
      </div>
      <div>Demo data — figures illustrative. Source attribution + confidence on every claim.</div>
    </footer>
  </main>

  <style>
    .expose-demo-entity {
      background-image: linear-gradient(transparent calc(100% - 2px), #0F3D2E calc(100% - 2px));
      background-size: 4px 100%;
      background-position: 0 100%;
      background-repeat: repeat-x;
      cursor: help;
      transition: background-color 0.15s ease;
    }
    .expose-demo-entity:hover {
      background-color: rgba(15, 61, 46, 0.08);
    }
  </style>
</LightLayout>
